WEBVTT

00:00:00.325 --> 00:00:02.167
Track 12.09

00:00:03.978 --> 00:00:04.931
Narrator: 1

00:00:05.758 --> 00:00:09.163
A: Would you like to come to my party on Saturday?

00:00:09.188 --> 00:00:12.039
B: I’d love to come. Thank you.

00:00:13.257 --> 00:00:14.138
Narrator: 2

00:00:15.117 --> 00:00:18.022
A: Would you like to go to the cinema on Thursday?

00:00:18.047 --> 00:00:20.414
B: Sorry, I’m busy then.

00:00:20.829 --> 00:00:22.276
But Friday’s OK.

00:00:22.301 --> 00:00:24.926
A: OK, we can go on Friday.

00:00:24.953 --> 00:00:25.842
B: Great!

00:00:27.567 --> 00:00:28.448
Narrator: 3

00:00:29.156 --> 00:00:31.959
A: Would you like to come for lunch at the weekend?

00:00:31.984 --> 00:00:34.914
B: I’d love to, but I’m away this weekend.

00:00:35.290 --> 00:00:36.957
A: Are you free next weekend?

00:00:36.982 --> 00:00:38.197
B: Yes, I am.

00:00:38.222 --> 00:00:39.706
A: You can come then!

00:00:39.731 --> 00:00:41.579
B: Thank you. I’d love to come.